dct_description_sm: Map of Great Britain and Ireland. Relief shown pictorially. Latin text on verso with caption title: Tabula I Europae. From: Claudii Ptolomæi Alexandrini mathematicor[um] principis, Opus geographi[a]e ... [Strasbourg]: Ioannes Grieninger ... opera et expensis proprijs id opus insigne, [a]ereis notulis excepit, laudabiliq[ue] fine perfecit, xii. die Marcij anno M.D. XXII.
